item.title: CVE-2021-24816|2024-08-03T19:42:17.200Z -- unknown -- phoenix%20media%20rename
item.description: The Phoenix Media Rename WordPress plugin before 3.4.4 does not have capability checks in its phoenix_media_rename AJAX action, which could allow users with Author roles to rename any uploaded media files, including ones they do not own.
